title: "SolveWatch AI"
abstract: >
  Real-time AI interview assistant featuring on-device Whisper STT,
  streaming LocalAgreement-2 transcription, multi-provider AI fallback
  (OpenAI / Groq / Gemini / Anthropic), and a stealth Electron HUD overlay
  that is excluded from all screen-capture tools via OS-level content protection.
